description: Int’l Street Cuizine is on a mission to serve LA  delicious foods found from all around this world. With their menu that offers a tasty variety of beef & seafood skewers, as well as a delectably eclectic menu that includes tortas, Korean BBQ, egg rolls, (and so much more), you get an exhilarating taste of a global adventure when you try anything from this super neat truck.
name: Int'l Street Cuizine
